body:
I fail to understand why I should get punished via the leaver buster for something that is 100% out of my control.

Due to issues with Nbn and providers all over Australia, plus recent issues with natural disasters damaging international lines between singapore and Hong Kong to Australia on top of the never ending upgrades etc to line infastructure, I keep losing connection at random points. I could be fine for hours without issue or I could have problems non stop. It varies so much, so why should I have to miss out on LoL because Leaver buster keeps pinging me. I think its unfair when I have no control on the situation and even the ISP don&#039;t know when the lines etc will be fixed or finished.

In my opinion unless someone actively reports me. i.e 2 people each game min for like 3 matches. I shouldn't be punished for something I cannot help. There is a difference between afk/quitting and losing connection all together!{{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}}
